"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"President Masoud Pezeshkian says Iran will not attack first, but Qatar's defense ministry says it has stopped a missile. The president also asks Tehran to choose new leaders who are acceptable to the White House after six days of war.\",            \"english_title\": \"Iran and Qatar Tensions\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente Masoud Pezeshkian dice que Ir\u00e1n no atacar\u00e1 primero, pero el ministerio de defensa de Qatar dice que ha detenido un misil. El presidente tambi\u00e9n pide a Teher\u00e1n que elija nuevos l\u00edderes que sean aceptables para la Casa Blanca despu\u00e9s de seis d\u00edas de guerra.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Tensiones entre Ir\u00e1n y Qatar\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The BBC reports that troops and tanks are gathering near the border, as people think Israel might be planning a big ground invasion to fight Hezbollah. Suspected Islamist militants took over a village for two days before troops and air strikes forced them out.\",            \"english_title\": \"Troops Near Border\",            \"translated_version\": \"La BBC informa que tropas y tanques se est\u00e1n reuniendo cerca de la frontera, ya que la gente piensa que Israel podr\u00eda estar planeando una gran invasi\u00f3n terrestre para luchar contra Hezbollah. Militantes islamistas sospechosos tomaron un pueblo durante dos d\u00edas antes de que las tropas y los ataques a\u00e9reos los obligaran a salir.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Tropas Cerca de la Frontera\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A drone attack on Azerbaijan has made it hard for airlines to decide how to deal with problems in the Gulf. Ukraine has started a program to use armed robots on the battlefield against Russian forces.\",            \"english_title\": \"Drone Attack and Armed Robots\",            \"translated_version\": \"Un ataque de dron en Azerbaiy\u00e1n ha hecho dif\u00edcil para las aerol\u00edneas decidir c\u00f3mo manejar problemas en el Golfo. Ucrania ha comenzado un programa para usar robots armados en el campo de batalla contra las fuerzas rusas.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ataque de Dron y Robots Armados\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Ukraine President Volodymyr Zelensky says ten other people, including children, are hurt as rescuers keep looking through the rubble.\",            \"english_title\": \"Injuries in Ukraine\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de Ucrania, Volodymyr Zelensky, dice que otras diez personas, incluidos ni\u00f1os, est\u00e1n heridas mientras los rescatistas siguen buscando entre los escombros.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Heridos en Ucrania\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"US President Donald Trump will meet with Latin American leaders who share his views to try and reduce China's influence in the region.\",            \"english_title\": \"Trump and Latin America\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de EE.UU., Donald Trump, se reunir\u00e1 con l\u00edderes de Am\u00e9rica Latina que comparten sus opiniones para intentar reducir la influencia de China en la regi\u00f3n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Trump y Am\u00e9rica Latina\"        }    ]}"